description: These text faces are angry but they are also kind of confused. They are raising their hands with the palms up and asking an elongated, “whhhyyyy?!” They just cannot believe what has happened and they find it to be the dumbest thing they have ever seen or heard. This anger is one of frustration, disbelief, and irritation.
